ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the Non-Article 5 North Atlantic Treaty Organization Medal for Service in relation to Operation
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the NON-ARTICLE 5 NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION (NATO) MEDAL called the NATO Vigilance Medal; and (2) directs that the Medal follow the Non-Article 5 NATO Medal for service on NATO operation ʺSEA GUARDIAN" in the order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
